# 🧪 Offline Practice Labs for Pentesting

All these labs can be set up and used **without subscriptions or internet**.

---

## 🔧 Vulnerable Machines

| Name | Description | Link |
|------|-------------|------|
| Metasploitable 2 | Classic Linux vulnerable OS | https://sourceforge.net/projects/metasploitable/ |
| DVWA | Web app for SQLi, XSS, File Upload | https://github.com/digininja/DVWA |
| Juice Shop | Modern web app for bug hunting | https://github.com/juice-shop/juice-shop |
| VulnHub | Realistic CTF-style VMs | https://www.vulnhub.com/ |
| OWASP BWA | Bundle of web apps (Mutillidae, WebGoat, DVWA) | https://sourceforge.net/projects/owaspbwa/ |

---

## 🧰 Tools You'll Need

- Kali Linux (Attacker OS)
- VirtualBox or VMware
- linPEAS / winPEAS
- Wireshark, Burp Suite, Nmap, Netcat

---

## 🔁 Sample Lab Setup

1. Create Host-Only Network in VirtualBox
2. Add:
   - Kali Linux VM
   - Metasploitable2 / DVWA VM
3. Test connectivity: `ping`, `nmap`
